unnormalised: Taka, tumkam TAN chi garaz poddteli, mhonnje, Tax Deduction and Collection Account Number. Tech ek 10 ankdanchem alphanumeric number ani tumchi company TDS deduct kortat zalear tem zaruchem. Udharonnak, tum tumchea pogaaracho bharpai kortat zalear, tumkam TDS deduct korchi poddteli ani tachekhatir tumkam TAN lagtelem. Tech vicharunk voch, tum sorkarache vatten tax ekthaai kortat ani TAN tumkam ek ekthaai korpi mhonn vollokh dita. Tech bhair, GSTIN, mhonnje tumcho Goods and Services Tax Identification Number, to-ui zaroori asa jar tumcho dhondo taxable vostu vo sevanchea vangdda deal korta zalear. Dor eka rajeak ek veglo code asta, mhonnje Maharashtra khatir 27 vo Delhi khatir 07 GSTIN-an. Mhonnun, jar tumchi company anek rajyanim cholta zalear, tumkam zaitim GSTIN lagtolim.
normalised: T-A-N mhonnlear Tax Deduction and Collection Account Number tumkam zai poddtolo. To dha ank'keancho alphanumeric number asta ani tumchi company T-D-S kapta zalear to zaroori. Udharonnak, tum pogaar dit zalear, tumkam T-D-S kapchem poddttolem ani te khatir tumkam T-A-N zai poddtolo. Oxem chintat ki tum sorkarache vatin kar ektta kortat ani T-A-N tumkam ektta korpi mhonn vollkhota. Tech bhaxen, G-S-T-I-N, mhonnlear Goods and Services Tax Identification Number, tumcho business taxable vostuncheo vo sevancheo vevhar korta zalear to-i zaroori. Dor eka rajyacho veg-vegllo code asta, je bhaxen Maharashtrakhatir satravis vo Delhikhatir shunya saat G-S-T-I-N-ant. Mhonnun, tumchi company ekahunik rajyamni cholta zalear, tumkam chod G-S-T-I-N zai poddtele.
